title: Complete the Square
text: Group terms: 9(x**2 + 8x) + 16(y**2 + y) $$=$$ $$-4$$. Then complete the square.

title: Divide to Get Standard Form
text: After completing the square: $$\frac{\left(x+4\right)^2}{9}$$ + $$\frac{\left(y+0.5\right)^2}{2.25}$$ $$=$$ $$1$$. Identify a $$=$$ $$3$$, $$b$$ $$=$$ $$1.5$$.
